955
01:16:07,138 --> 01:16:08,942
Dia tak ingin hotel menghilang.

956
01:16:09,238 --> 01:16:13,482
Kemudian dia mungkin memberikanya
kepada Man Weol.

957
01:16:16,877 --> 01:16:19,417
Jika dia minum itu

958
01:16:19,417 --> 01:16:21,848
