967
01:17:09,768 --> 01:17:11,568
Jibaein-nim, Yu Na.

968
01:17:11,568 --> 01:17:14,313
Aku tahu.
Di mana Jang Man Weol?

969
01:17:41,068 --> 01:17:43,843
Pada hari pertamaku diikat ke Pohon Bulan,

970
01:17:46,907 --> 01:17:49,652
